    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be sure to follow Burst! on Kickstarter at  --campaign launching in February 2026!<br><br>**BURST! IS STILL IN EARLY DEVELOPMENT, ALL ART SUBJECT TO CHANGE AS WE REFINE THE GAME!**</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Burst! is the science-powered rhythm game where players blow up fireworks to the beat while swapping out Periodic Table elements to change the explosion colors!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111480/extras/af136a086a7bd985b5c417831455553f.poster.avif?t=1761164445\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111480/extras/af136a086a7bd985b5c417831455553f.webm?t=1761164445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111480/extras/af136a086a7bd985b5c417831455553f.mp4?t=1761164445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will meet the bird, BOP, who won a firework stand in an online auction. They'll then put on firework shows to wow crowds and raise the prominence of BOP's stand to increase the amount of explosion types, explosion colors and songs for the stand!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111480/extras/600bd3ff468f119fff72ffc492dbae89.avif?t=1761164445\" width=600 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Burst! is currently in early beta, and beginning the process of polish and refining. Burst! is also the first-ever video game to be supported by the Montana Film Office with a Big Sky Film Grant! Be sure to wishlist Burst! right here so you can follow our development journey for the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111480/extras/e26ccd23c03ffdbaccc1d8d74d2f6ca6.poster.avif?t=1761164445\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111480/extras/e26ccd23c03ffdbaccc1d8d74d2f6ca6.webm?t=1761164445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111480/extras/e26ccd23c03ffdbaccc1d8d74d2f6ca6.mp4?t=1761164445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starting March 18th, 2023, you can reserve a BOP Plushie by Makeship at .</p>",
